{eq}\begin{aligned}   A&=\$10,000{{\left( 1+\frac{0.1}{1} \right)}^{1*20}} \\   &=\$10,000{{\left( 1.1 \right)}^{20}} \\   &=\$10,000\times 6.72749 \\   &=\$67274.9 \\   &=\$67,275  \end{aligned}

